{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_07_03",
  "title": "kana 3話 お子様はチョロくていいねぇ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（か、kanaさんが白い粉まみれになってる）\n（一体、こころと何があったって言うんだ……！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（K-Kana-san is covered in white powder.）\n（What in the world happened with Kokoro…?!!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "んー？　何よ、そんなに慌てて\nまだ収録が始まるまで時間はあるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? What is it? Why are you in such a hurry?\nThere's still time before the recording starts‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.5060313861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "その……こころと怒鳴り合ってたとか物音がしてたとか\n聞いたもので、急ぎ駆けつけたんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… I heard you were yelling at Kokoro and there was a loud noise‚\nso I rushed over here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "……あー、そういうこと\n別に、こころにクッキーの焼き方教えてただけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ I see.\nNothing much‚ I was just teaching Kokoro how to bake cookies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2117685955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.8934691429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "物音ってのは多分、料理道具をまとめて床に落とした音\n金属製のボウルとか、確かに凄い音してたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The noise was probably the sound of all the cooking utensils being dropped on the floor at once.\nMetal bowls and such‚ they certainly made a loud noise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3451019288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……お菓子？　二人で作ってたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Snacks? You two were making them together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2356453896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.9841487568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "そ。こころのやつ難易度高いのばっかり作りたがるから\nまずは簡単なやつからやらせてみたんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. That Kokoro brat always wants to make only high-difficulty things.\nI tried having her start with something simple first‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらまあ、あいつ、計量雑だわ道具は床に落とすわ\nしかもkanaに向かって小麦粉ぶちまけるわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ then‚ that brat was sloppy with the measuring‚ dropped the utensils on the floor‚\nand on top of that‚ she threw flour at me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.0602719626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.6567099573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "まー、kanaがフォロー入れてやって\n最終的にはちゃんと美味しく出来ましたけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I stepped in to help her out‚\nbut in the end‚ we did manage to make something delicious~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4602719626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.2833564443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういうことですか……\nでもクッキー作りなんて、なんでいきなり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-So that's what happened…\nBut why baking cookies all of a sudden?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "この間、番組のコーナーの企画出してくれって\nプロデューサーが言ってたでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The producer asked me the other day\nfor a program segment idea‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1849686942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.2480959258
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "どうせならお菓子作りとかどうかなって思ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought‚ why not try baking sweets or something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2480959258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.1716796718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "実際にモノになるか分からないから\nこころにも試しにやらせてみたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I wasn't sure if it would actually work out‚\nI had Kokoro try it out as a test.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6849686942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことでしたか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what happened…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1911808493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.7535062475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "あんたがなんで焦ってたのかは想像つくけど\nどうせ番組が打ち切りになりそうとか思ったんでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can imagine why you were panicking‚ but\nyou probably thought the show was going to be canceled or something‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7139607591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "あんたにご心配いただかなくても\nこんな大きい仕事、ふいにするような真似するかっての",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even without your worry‚\ndo you think I'd mess up such a big job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.4472940924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.8024409614
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ですよね。……でも、kanaさんからお菓子作りを\n提案したっていうのは、ちょっと意外でしたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. …But‚ I was a little surprised that Kana-san\nsuggested baking sweets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.7251393957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "こころがさぁ、最近、相棒とあんまり話せてないとか\nkanaとばっかり仕事してて、怒ってないかなとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ you know‚ has been saying she hasn't talked much with her partner lately‚\nor that she's worried if Ai is angry because she's only been working with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1699925266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "しょげてて鬱陶しいからさぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was moping around and it was annoying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1743907931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "相棒……ああ、愛のことですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Partner… Ah‚ you mean Ai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.172644814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.172644814
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.715116668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "お菓子でも作って、番組で作ったの～って持ってったら\n話しやすいんじゃないのって言ってみたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought if she made some snacks and brought them‚ saying‚ \"I made these on the show~\"\nit might be easier for them to talk‚ so I suggested it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5124643806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "思った以上に食いついてきたから\nあ、これ企画にして出してやろうと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She took the bait more than I expected.\nSo I thought‚ \"Ah‚ I'll turn this into a segment idea.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.8614748402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.3772350393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん、こころのこと心配してくれてたんですね\nやっぱり二人は仲がい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kana-san‚ you were worried about Kokoro.\nYou two really are friends…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.7684347871
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "……にしても、あいつ、目をきらきらさせててさぁ\nお子様はチョロくていいねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But still‚ that brat had her eyes sparkling.\nKids are so easy to please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.5036641284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.0927885137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_03-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "ま、これであいつ、kanaに頭上がらなくなったし～\nこれで番組もkanaのものってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ with this‚ she won't be able to boss me around anymore~\nNow the show is mine too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.3036641284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
